com.badlogic.gdx.graphics.g3d.particles

Class ParticleChannels

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.badlogic.gdx.graphics.g3d.particles.ParticleChannels

  • public class ParticleChannels
extends java.lang.Object
    This contains all the definitions of particle related channels and channel initializers. It is also used by the ParticleController to handle temporary channels allocated by influencers.
    Author:
    inferno
